Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:18.49,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:28.46,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:33.56,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:38.53,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:51.14,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:01:00.84,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:11.35,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:20.65,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:33.15,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:55.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:56.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Main armament, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance, 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell. HE round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Loading complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:16.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:29.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Signal the forces to our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit destroyed. Take up our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:33.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, it's Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My. Then let's have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:07.36,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}A Mountain Hike - The End of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back on your feet again, aren't you, Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:18.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely healed, but she just won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this place is just wonderful, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:25.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she run around like that when it's so hot out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:39.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's your mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And one for you, Noël. From the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His first name is Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His last name is Fessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Common names in the Sept region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Mr. Fessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful that you have friends from so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:34.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:43.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Noël! I almost believed you for a second there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Klaus something for the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are our orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:41.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:48.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:06:00.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you for everything every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll take care of the place while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:32.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck out there, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on a field trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound great, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A field trip? Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:56.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just walking would be a bit boring, so let's play a little game while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, all along the southern edges of Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:05.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, the border between Seize and Nomansland,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,there are surveillance devices from the ancient past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of these, three are due for regular maintenance checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:18.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to look at them during our field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission's not even disguised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just your normal field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything even if they were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noctur-Type Surveillance Devices are a complete black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what he meant by "Good luck out there."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But just walking is putting time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,will be carrying those on your backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:08:02.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. To carry something like this, you have to put your body weight forward and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Botcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:23.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all such good children. You've met all of our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:30.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! When you're lifting a heavy pack, first you lie back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:38.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then once the full weight of the pack is on your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:55.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'kit cha chappin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:08.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Now then. Filicia and I will go ahead to the goal point on your map and wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:12.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If at any point you don't think you can go on, blow your bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:22.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are wild animals on this mountain. Should you encounter one, in order to handle the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I authorize the use of firearms,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun now, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,March!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:18.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy! Too heavy! Too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it gets heavier every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, how much farther?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In working order. No abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on. That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:39.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that I thought about this machine protecting the town all alone, all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Noël, where's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Th- Th- That mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:17.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:22.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone do something about these packs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:59.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. The Commander and Rio both hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say something, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:36.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so refreshing! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,R&R!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:09.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone says, we are getting R&R! Because I say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, this is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a field trip. We have to make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget about those stupidly-heavy sacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is training!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Filicia said-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, are you blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's black-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Blacker than coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But her hair is blonde and her skin is so white and she's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's good about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:35.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are talking about a different Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:39.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Someone do something about this pair of airheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, time for food! Time for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll dry soon with this sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our food is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was a boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in my village, they dug up our fields pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a lot of food during the summer, so they usually wouldn't come near.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:14.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The compass is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay to leave those sacks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:28.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first priority should be reaching the goal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we headed in the right direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first device was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The river was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The second device is at the summit of the mountain we're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just need to head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! No matter what-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's anything we can eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:04.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sweet, a little sour, and just delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't climb up that. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:16.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:27.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Major Klaus once crossed a desert in a tank without food or water for three days and took down an enemy fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an amazing person...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Klaus is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bayberries...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just where is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten pretty dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to get our bearings after every turn, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "probably"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:44.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a compass, I can't be completely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? We walked all this way for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:54.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If the compass was that important, you should have kept it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not start fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:02.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for playing in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:14.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always spacing out and smiling like an idiot! That's why we're in this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:15.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Well, it looks like they'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:25.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you! I got you, so get off me! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomansland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:54.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of the world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:05.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I apologize! We were unable to complete the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What mission are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was for you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the signatures of those who came before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:25.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Every girl who comes to the fortress has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:32.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And has seen this. The end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our past, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:41.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk just a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:48.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing they left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:13.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:16.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like coming back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:31.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:32.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:47.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was worth the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:57.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:01.38,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:19.14,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:25.23,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:34.01,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:38.61,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.24,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:44.58,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:45.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:51.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:57.60,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:57.60,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:03.60,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:09.44,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:14.39,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:25.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Kanata's Day Off - A Haircut\N
